### Accounts — balances and ledger history. Self-contained: run top to bottom.

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### My accounts → captures the first (SAVINGS) account id
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {%
    client.assert(response.body.length > 0, "expected at least one account");
    client.global.set("accountId", response.body[0].id);
%}

### Transaction history (paginated ledger, newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Another user's / unknown account → 404 (existence is not leaked)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
